## Rules (her zaman uy — bunlar rules/ klasorunde detaylidir)
- Commit atmadan once tum testler gecmeli (project.conf: `CMD_TEST`)
- `main` branch'e direkt commit yok — her zaman feature branch
- Fonksiyon basina max satir (project.conf: `MAX_FUNCTION_LINES`)
- Component/dosya basina max satir (project.conf: `MAX_FILE_LINES`)
- Her yeni component/modul icin mutlaka test dosyasi yaz

## Subagentlar
Asagidaki subagentlari uygun durumlarda otomatik devreye al:
- `@planner` -> Yeni feature baslamadan once plan cikar
- `@architect` -> Mimari kararlar, klasor yapisi degisiklikleri
- `@tdd-guide` -> Test yaz, sonra implementation
- `@code-reviewer` -> Implementasyon bittikten sonra review
- `@deployer` -> Commit, push ve deploy islemleri (her adimda onay zorunlu)

## Skills (auto-invoked)
- `implement-feature` -> planner -> architect -> tdd-guide -> implement -> review -> deploy pipeline
- `deploy-pipeline` -> commit -> push -> deploy (her adimda onay zorunlu)
- `tdd` -> Test yazma workflow'u
- `refactor-clean` -> Dead code temizleme
- `codemap-update` -> Codebase haritasini guncelle

## Commands
- `/implement-feature` -> Feature gelistirme pipeline'ini baslat
- `/deploy` -> Deploy pipeline'ini baslat
- `/tdd` -> TDD workflow'u baslat
- `/refactor-clean` -> Temizlik workflow'u
- `/codemap-update` -> Codemap guncelle

